[Name] KVIrc
[Summary] Enhanced visual IRC client for X11/KDE
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] KVirc is a Visual Internet Relay Chat Client based on the Qt library. Features include a MDI user interface, drag & drop, built-in scripting language (aliases, popups and events), customizable backgrounds and colours, DCC (chat, send with resume, voice), CTCP functions, mIRC colour support with preview, notify list, online help and configurable logging.
[Homepage] http://www.kvirc.net/
